column5: Happy birthday Dave.  Hope you have a great day, Insert birthday cake here >      <    lol  Nautifish.
Happy B-Day Bud!!! You don't act a day over 12!!! (don't ever stop, boys will be boys)
Hope you have a super birthday Dave  21 again right  Joey
Happy Birthday "BIG" guy.  Enjoy yer day bud.
Happy Birthday to you, May you have many more years, and catch fish in every one of em
Hey Dave, Happy Happy, I hope you had a great day!  Maureen
All the 'Best' to you today Dave,and many many more to ya............

Happy Birthday Dave.  Nice show today as well - those pike sure can get in the way of the walleye fishing eh   Really appreciate the adjustments you make as well and showing how a day on the water doesn't always go how you plan it.
All the best and thanks for the shirt!
